{"content":[{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"超级个体的进化日志 - 2024年12月10日"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><b>真正的魔法，是科学中的科学。</b></span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;——《攻壳qiào机动队》"},"common":{"quote":true}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"能不能像黑客帝国一样，想学习什么知识，只需要躺着睡一觉就行了？"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"很遗憾的是，答案是否定的。"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"虽然目前咱们有了很多以前科幻作品中才有的技术，比如AI和脑机接口，但还是不能实现大量知识秒加载的效果。"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"但如果利用好AI这个强大的助手 + 科学的学习方法，还是能做到一些以前不敢想象的事情的。"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"比如，从0基础快速入门JavaScript编程语言，构建自己的网站和应用；使用智能Agent，搭建高度DIY工作流的问答机器人，这都是有可能实现的。"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"在高频使用Cursor帮助我学习编程后，分享几点干货体验："},"common":{}},{"key":"list","data":{"style":"unordered","items":[{"content":"老生常谈：不要给自己设限。这个时代让每个人都具备快速迭代认知和技术的能力，你不该开始时就否认自己的可能性","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"你需要知道自己想去哪儿，才会找到通往目标的路","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"AI改变了编程学习的流程和知识的检索方法","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"借助Cursor，你可以先构建出网站/应用，再去学习构建的方法","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"GitHub + Serverless服务 快速部署项目。构建即思考，创造即学习","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"分享也是一种费曼方法","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"AI实在对产品人太友好了。你会分析需求，就能构建出产品，再迭代改进产品体验。AI可以帮你设计和开发","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"如果想成为一个超级个体，一定要及早建立自己的自媒体矩阵。公众号应该是第一站","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]},{"content":"有人的地方就有江湖。自媒体也是一样。你要学习一些基本礼仪。","style":"unordered","closed":false,"items":[]}]},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":2,"content":"Orca-Note 第一时间体验 第二期"},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1733529427131-image-4t0dye1tkuc2k.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor2.0/images/2024-12-7/1733529427131-image-4t0dye1tkuc2k.png"},"caption":"Orca-Note | 虎鲸笔记","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"上期我们第一时间向粉丝推荐了Orca-Note | 虎鲸笔记，反响不错。今天我们接着来聊一聊虎鲸笔记"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"随着虎鲸笔记的深入使用，我愈发感受到这款软件的优秀。"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"在虎鲸笔记上，我能看到巨人的影子——Roam Research、Logseq、LogseqDB……"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"我们又能看到虎鲸笔记对笔记系统自己的理解和发展：大纲笔记和长文模式无缝切换"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"上次漏写了虎鲸笔记一个重要的功能，这次补上：虎鲸标签体系"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":3,"content":"虎鲸标签"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"虎鲸笔记的标签体系非常有特点，我们可以看一下软件的录屏："},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1733531057990-orca-note02.gif","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor2.0/images/2024-12-7/1733531057990-orca-note02.gif"},"caption":"orca-note02.gif","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<footnote data-note=\"下载链接 GitHub: https://github.com/sethyuan/orca-note/releases  中文ReadMe：https://github.com/sethyuan/orca-note/blob/main/README.zh.md\" data-title=\"\">虎鲸笔记</footnote>的标签系统是具有“属性”功能的高级标签，可以通过“#标签”快速输入，并对标签属性进行编辑。这是一个很有探索价值的高级功能。"},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":2,"content":"玉伯的<footnote data-note=\"https://youmind.ai/\" data-title=\"\">YouMind.ai</footnote>开始接受预订"},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1733531269561-image-b1y6qt0nxadyc.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor2.0/images/2024-12-7/1733531269561-image-b1y6qt0nxadyc.png"},"caption":"YouMind.ai","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"这是一个AI知识管理的web应用，由玉伯团队精心打造。可以对YouTube视频进行快速添加AI脚本、生成美观方便的大纲"},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1733531417526-image-o8cptd4tybuxz.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor2.0/images/2024-12-7/1733531417526-image-o8cptd4tybuxz.png"},"caption":"YouMind.ai","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1733531433346-image-aotciiajeqzmy.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor2.0/images/2024-12-7/1733531433346-image-aotciiajeqzmy.png"},"caption":"IBM一个7分钟的视频，讲透什么是机器学习、深度学习","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"利用YouMind.ai，可以帮助学习者快速刷视频，了解技术；可以实时与AI进行对话、总结。"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"可以看得出，这是个提高学习效率的神器"},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"目前价格也很美丽，200rmb一年的订阅费"},"common":{}},{"key":"image","data":{"image":{"assetName":"1733531890184-image.png","url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Neonity2020/geekeditor2.0/images/2024-12-7/1733531890184-image.png"},"caption":"YouMind.ai","withCaption":true},"common":{}},{"key":"header","data":{"level":2,"content":"参考"},"common":{}},{"key":"footnote","data":{"items":[{"title":"","note":"下载链接 GitHub: https://github.com/sethyuan/orca-note/releases  中文ReadMe：https://github.com/sethyuan/orca-note/blob/main/README.zh.md"},{"title":"","note":"https://youmind.ai/"}]},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":""},"common":{}}],"typeset":"typeset-1687836132043","layout":"web","basic":{"title":"","cover":"","summary":""}}